# SAFE add-on list (200+ patterns) for clean repos with reduced risk of hiding real content.
# IMPORTANT: This file is meant to be appended to your existing .gitignore.
# It intentionally avoids global media ignores like *.png/*.jpg/*.mp4 because those
# can hide real artwork/assets.

########################################
# Additional OS/editor junk (extra)
########################################
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db?
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
.DS_Store.*
Icon
Icon?
*.swp
